  <description type="morphology">Petiole  glabrous, not viscid-glandular.  Blade  thin and herbaceous, sometimes thick (but not leathery), not viscid-glandular, abaxially densely white-farinose, adaxially glabrous.  Distal pinnae  mostly regularly lobed.  Proximal basiscopic lobes  of basal pinnae pinnatifid, often deeply so.</description>
